data.description: **4.99% ASSUMABLE VA Mortgage if Buyer's entitlement is transferable ~OR~ Seller will pay $5000 towards Buyers Closing Costs or it can be used to buy down interest rate! BETTER THAN NEW CHATOOGA PLAN with 4 Bedrooms & 3 Full Baths. Upstairs you have a full bedroom w/ensuite bath. There is a Lg Family room w/Natural Gas Fireplace open to the kitchen with a Lg sit down breakfast bar w/beautiful Pendant lighting overhead, SS Appliances to include a gas cooktop, In-wall oven and microwave, also a Lg walk in Pantry and so much more. The Seller added premium LVP Flooring throughout the main floor. NO Carpet Downstairs. The Custom cabinets are covered w/a beautiful timeless granite. The master bath has an upgraded tiled shower to the ceiling w/upgraded plumbing fixtures and shower door, a jetted tub and very lg. walk in closet. There is a natural gas tankless hot water heater, rain gutters, screened in patio with door to the beautifully landscaped back yard with a stained privacy fence. ALL THE IMPORTANT UPGRADES HAVE BEEN ADDED BY THE HOMEOWNER. A COUNTER DEPTH REFRIGERATOR IS IN THE HOME AND IS NEGOTIABLE.
